\" />"},{"pid":"0a70a6df4074b1195b55b0457b22e5e1f3edbffd","tid":2089472,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T16:55:57.000Z","msg":"推 tweet國際戰線 天下制裁<br />\nBNO已開通 MPF準備走人"},{"pid":"c0c30f277dffa050cd2960a66d190d9662b8bbf4","tid":2089472,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T16:56:09.000Z","msg":"推 國際戰線 全面配合制裁<br />\n舉報輸入軍民兩用科技設備公司"},{"pid":"26a04c1ef2532e1b7fb8eee9784b1b0306e0fae0","tid":2089472,"uid":237487,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T16:56:28.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">同埋佢啲仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"8df616434c4ff4ff92f0e12cbbde0c6200ed1e6b","tid":2089472,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T16:56:35.000Z","msg":"借個位，BNO平權正視聽<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">黑色五毛分化警告，大量五毛正在用藍絲有BNO、走人對唔住97後割97後等風向進行分化</span></span></strong>，大家小心。<br />\n<br />\n1.<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大家比人拉過/有小朋友（細路是重點，香港未來棟樑，正如今時今日d前線義士，咪比佢地洗腦變小糞紅，否則香港係真正玩完）的話就應該即刻走</span></span></strong>，其他人亦應該起碼做好隨時走既準備，<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">香港抗爭運動已經由本土抗爭升級為準國際戰爭， 我們能做的十分有限。 相反大家離開或準備好隨時可以離開，則美國及其盟友可以隨時採取行動，對香港進行制裁，令香港達至零經濟活動，攬炒香港經濟， 甚至日後作出軍事行動亦無需擔心誤傷香港人。</span></span></strong> 而且大家亦可用移民理由提取所有資產及強積金進一步<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">打擊香港的財政儲備</span></span></strong>。<br />\n而且多人走亦可以起到掩護最需要走既手足，救奶左野手足係目前最重要既事。<br />\n<br />\n2.大家<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">無需擔心藍絲以及黑警移民英國</span></span></strong>，藍絲得兩種a.垃圾b.收成期，a.涯唔到六年移民監b.揾錢唔捨得走/走要承受巨大損失<br />\n<br />\n重點：大家<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不應該反對平權或推到現階段設立篩選，因為這樣會妨礙奶左野手足逃難</span></span></strong>。反而，大家應該在藍絲移民英國後再篤灰。大家，要記住，<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">篤灰係一把藍絲頭上既利劍，一日未入籍一日都嚮度，我就係要佢地嚮英國每一日都擔心比人篤灰，呢樣恐懼做為懲罰先係最大懲罰</span></span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n3.<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">97後手足唔會被割</span></span></strong>，首先，佢地可以跟BNO父母及配偶前往英國。第二，對於<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">未受BNO平權保障嘅人佢哋仲有美國既救生艇計劃</span></span></strong>，該計劃估計幾日內亦會通過。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">希望樓主可以pin，一齊擊退五毛</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"2270657a81fb5799c77c83f48d52ac947d80bd1f","tid":2089472,"uid":20870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T16:57:08.000Z","msg":"劍橋戰線！"},{"pid":"f49457e5695ff0ae6157b60310f3c81fea2b4a78","tid":2089472,"uid":263648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fbf0de63d475d69a391c654256a9ee0a07503f1f","tid":2089472,"uid":97944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T16:34:01.000Z","msg":"特首林鄭月娥是劍橋大學沃爾森學院榮譽院士，去年至今英國上議院議員、在英港人曾要求學院褫奪林鄭榮譽院士的名銜。沃爾森學院今日（1日）表示，堅決支持保障人權及言論自由，學院對《港區國安法》頒布後，對香港最近發生的事件深表關切。學院指，會考慮褫奪林鄭月娥榮譽院士的名銜（will be considering Mrs Lam's position as an Honorary Fellow of the College）。<br />\n<br />\n三名英國上議院議員去年 11 月去信劍橋大學校長、副校長及沃爾森學院院長，要求收回林鄭月娥榮譽院士頭銜。三名議員在信中批評，林鄭無能及好鬥的處事方式，引發200萬人走上街頭示威。該信又斥林鄭多次作出錯誤決定，包括是DQ民主派參選人，以及囚禁社運人士等。同月，超過170名學生、校友及市民在當地發起遊行，促請劍橋校方撤銷林鄭月娥的榮譽院士頭銜。<br />\n<br />\n劍橋大學曾在去年 11 月表示，沒有打算對作出任何行動，亦表明會避免作進一步公眾評論。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T16:57:58.000Z","msg":"買定花生先。睇劍橋被港共blacklist。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac151a050d11dbf4167d3e36242dd895d4e7c33d","tid":2089472,"uid":79355,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T16:58:03.000Z","msg":"仲考慮乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b8ffba04520d04234cda23e092ed0090d88d420","tid":2089472,"uid":97944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"669f86e6802a9fe4d291a7686206f50c5f377a4a","tid":2089472,"uid":37413,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T16:40:34.000Z","msg":"鄭林兆波呢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T16:58:07.000Z","msg":"佢係手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c6f6c0fe9cce0107fba044a63d7ebf629fdec80","tid":2089472,"uid":239392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T16:58:19.000Z","msg":"無所謂啦，都就快聞到棺材香"},{"pid":"b5dd781aebcee97fdf5587508ff61361dcd61923","tid":2089472,"uid":97944,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"81adec21eb1be9713270fc6512feed05dc1fcb55","tid":2089472,"uid":123988,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T16:44:09.000Z","msg":"請問有無得推Twitter?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T16:58:56.000Z","msg":"好似無twitter post<br />\n唔知luke de pulford會唔會提呢件事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8551572eadc249ea972143d63acbdc318acfbd5d","tid":2089472,"uid":79382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T16:59:08.000Z","msg":"其實要考慮啲咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5f3452d498245e0c5e14b78798dac72931579cc","tid":2089472,"uid":97944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9b067ead056667d88993e326c457f11563d16ec2","tid":2089472,"uid":88743,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T16:44:17.000Z","msg":"林鄭會唔會話：<br />\n沃爾森學院此舉已違反《港版國安法》<im